    <title>rocketmq 单机安装部署调试</title>
    <link href="https://tisboy.github.io/2017/10/21/rocketmq-1/"/>
    <id>https://tisboy.github.io/2017/10/21/rocketmq-1/</id>
    <published>2017-10-20T17:15:55.000Z</published>
    <updated>2017-10-20T17:28:42.600Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>参考文档：<a href="http://rocketmq.apache.org/docs/quick-start/" target="_blank" rel="external">http://rocketmq.apache.org/docs/quick-start/</a></p><h1 id="Clone-amp-Build"><a href="#Clone-amp-Build" class="headerlink" title="Clone &amp; Build"></a>Clone &amp; Build</h1><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">&gt; git <span class="built_in">clone</span> -b develop https://github.com/apache/rocketmq.git</div><div class="line">&gt; <span class="built_in">cd</span> rocketmq</div><div class="line">&gt; mvn -Prelease-all -DskipTests clean install -U</div><div class="line">&gt; <span class="built_in">cd</span> distribution/target/apache-rocketmq</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="import-idea"><a href="#import-idea" class="headerlink" title="import idea"></a>import idea</h1><p>目录结构如下：<br><img src="images/1508518474316.jpg" alt="enter description here"></p><h1 id="Start-Name-Server"><a href="#Start-Name-Server" class="headerlink" title="Start Name Server"></a>Start Name Server</h1><p> 设置环境变量：<br> ROCKETMQ_HOME=C:\dev\RocketMQ\rocketmq\distribution\target\apache-rocketmq<br> 如图所示：<br> <img src="images/1508518732287.jpg" alt="enter description here"></p><h1 id="Start-Broker"><a href="#Start-Broker" class="headerlink" title="Start Broker"></a>Start Broker</h1><p>设置参数和环境变量：<br><img src="images/1508518926627.jpg" alt="enter description here"></p><h1 id="Test"><a href="#Test" class="headerlink" title="Test"></a>Test</h1><p> 运行 rocketmq\example\src\main\java\org\apache\rocketmq\example\quickstart 目录下的Consumer和Producer</p><p> 运行结果图如下：<br> <img src="images/1508519399611.jpg" alt="enter description here"></p><p><img src="images/1508519440322.jpg" alt="enter description here"></p>]]></content>
    
